Heart rate 110, 140 over 56, right
arm, 100 over palp, left. Respiration's 18.

80
00:05:10,243 --> 00:05:13,145
Gave him nitro...
Dissecting aortic aneurysm.

81
00:05:15,015 --> 00:05:16,039
Mateo?

82
00:05:17,751 --> 00:05:19,344
Hope you're on your
game today, Floyd.

83
00:05:21,922 --> 00:05:23,720
Who's... Mateo Fernandez.

84
