to stop taking my stuff.

182
00:09:57,831 --> 00:09:58,855
Incoming!

183
00:10:03,103 --> 00:10:04,503
Rib spreader. Rib spreader.

184
00:10:04,604 --> 00:10:06,266
Fair warning. This
is being recorded

185
00:10:06,339 --> 00:10:09,537
so that Dr. Fernandez can see
my technique when he's awake.

186
00:10:10,210 --> 00:10:11,678
Um...

187
00:10:11,778 --> 00:10:16,716
Dr. Reynolds? Uh...
Dr. Bloom asked me to, um...

188
