Start with the
subject, then the verb,

189
00:10:19,953 --> 00:10:21,633
and see where the
sentence goes from there.

190
00:10:22,689 --> 00:10:24,783
The cases from Baptist
are crowding the ED.

191
00:10:24,858 --> 00:10:26,349
There's a pleurodesis.

192
00:10:26,626 --> 00:10:28,270
With your permission, I
was thinking I could grab

193
00:10:28,294 --> 00:10:30,490
a general attending to
supervise and handle it myself.

194
00:10:30,563 --> 00:10:33,226
Appreciate the enthusiasm, but
prep the patient and wait for me.

195
00:10:33,700 --> 00:10:34,977
It's just the ED's awfully full,

196
00:10:35,001 --> 00:10:36,367
and I really think
I can help out.

197
00:10:36,469 --> 00:10:37,749
You have a very
promising future.

198
00:10:37,971 --> 00:10:40,691
I don't want you in over your head
when I'm too busy to bail you out.

199
00:10:40,807 --> 00:10:43,003
A mistake like that can
derail your entire career,

200
00:10:43,076 --> 00:10:46,171
so go ahead and prep the patient,
and I'll get there when I'm done.

201
00:10:47,747 --> 00:10:48,806
Yes, sir.

202
00:10:49,816 --> 00:10:50,875
Thank you.

203
00:10:53,253 --> 00:10:55,552
Baptist's surgeons are on a
flight back from San Diego.

204
00:10:55,655 --> 00:10:57,851
It lands in five hours.
You got this, right?

205
00:10:57,924 --> 00:10:59,358
Do I have a choice?

206
00:10:59,425 --> 00:11:01,360
I could warp the
space-time continuum.

207
00:11:01,895 --> 00:11:03,363
Hey, what patient is that for?

208
00:11:03,696 --> 00:11:04,823
Homeless woman outside.

209
00:11:05,098 --> 00:11:06,575
You couldn't find a
patient inside to help?

210
00:11:06,599 --> 00:11:09,034
If I don't help her, she's
gonna lose her foot.

211
00:11:09,369 --> 00:11:10,393
Send an intern.

212
00:11:10,503 --> 00:11:13,598
She's skeptical of doctors and so
am I, so we have an understanding.

213
00:11:13,706 --> 00:11:15,072
I'll be back in five
minutes. What?

214
00:11:16,376 --> 00:11:17,537
Sorry, Doc!

215
00:11:21,948 --> 00:11:23,917
You and Ella have an
asymmetric power structure.

216
00:11:24,017 --> 00:11:26,077
Giving her a gift
can be misinterpreted

217
00:11:26,186 --> 00:11:30,214
as a deliberate extraction of
reciprocal favors, sexual or otherwise.

218
00:11:30,290 --> 00:11:31,952
I see you talked to Dr. Frome.

219
00:11:34,961 --> 00:11:37,692
Mrs. Monaghan, I am
Dr. Vijay Kapoor and this is Dr...

220
00:11:37,764 --> 00:11:38,788
Kao. Dr. Kao.

221
00:11:40,133 --> 00:11:43,035
I'm dizzy. I'm so
sorry to hear that.

222
00:11:43,703 --> 00:11:45,228
