00:12:55,975 --> 00:12:57,102
I know.

247
00:12:57,176 --> 00:12:59,202
Volt Cola spend millions
each year to defeat

248
00:12:59,312 --> 00:13:01,713
public health legislation
that could actually help.

249
00:13:02,048 --> 00:13:03,107
I know.

250
00:13:03,182 --> 00:13:05,761
So, unless you want to hurry along
the epidemic of childhood obesity,

251
00:13:05,785 --> 00:13:07,545
then there's no way
you can take their money.

252
00:13:07,854 --> 00:13:08,981
I know. Great.

253
00:13:09,055 --> 00:13:12,321
Now you can focus on the
epidemic of overcrowding in my ED.

