00:13:26,873 --> 00:13:27,897
Can you feel this?

259
00:13:28,007 --> 00:13:29,305
No. How about this?

260
00:13:29,409 --> 00:13:30,536
Mmm-mmm.

261
00:13:30,643 --> 00:13:32,737
She was in pain,
so we called 911.

262
00:13:33,413 --> 00:13:35,177
We didn't want to
take any chances.

263
00:13:35,248 --> 00:13:37,217
Should we have just
driven her to Baptist?

264
00:13:37,317 --> 00:13:38,597
No, no. You did the right thing.

265
