00:13:46,592 --> 00:13:48,527
I need for the biopsy right now.

270
00:13:48,594 --> 00:13:51,063
Those are gonna tell
you if my cancer's back?

271
00:13:51,364 --> 00:13:52,491
That's right.

272
00:13:56,769 --> 00:13:58,431
What's it like when you die?

