275
00:14:10,350 --> 00:14:11,750
All right, baby girl?

276
00:14:12,585 --> 00:14:13,883
Right, Dr. Sharpe?

277
00:14:16,289 --> 00:14:19,691
Do you want the elephant
or the tiger Band-Aid?

278
00:14:20,526 --> 00:14:22,017
Nobody tells me anything.

279
00:14:32,872 --> 00:14:35,535
Miss me? Nope, nope, nope, nope.

280
00:14:35,608 --> 00:14:38,544
I can't afford your
help! My help is free.

281
00:14:40,380 --> 00:14:42,542
Not taking it is gonna
cost you your foot,

282
00:14:42,615 --> 00:14:45,050
so either way, you're
gonna have to deal with me.

283
00:14:46,786 --> 00:14:48,254
You're relentless.

284
00:14:49,489 --> 00:14:50,548
I'm Max.

285
00:14:54,160 --> 00:14:56,493
I'm Faye. It's nice
to meet you, Faye.

286
00:14:58,164 --> 00:15:02,898
Okay, take one of these a
day until the bottle is gone.

287
00:15:03,669 --> 00:15:07,731
I have to go, but, uh, I'll
come back to check on you.

288
00:15:11,277 --> 00:15:13,940
I have a brother
who's very sick.

289
00:15:17,350 --> 00:15:18,818
