294
00:16:00,626 --> 00:16:01,992
You have to see him.

295
00:16:14,373 --> 00:16:15,397
This way.

296
00:16:26,552 --> 00:16:28,297
Hey, how much longer?
I'm backing up downstairs.

297
00:16:28,321 --> 00:16:29,865
I'm holding this
man's aorta together

