00:16:38,030 --> 00:16:39,110
I'm going as fast as I can.

303
00:16:39,165 --> 00:16:40,445
I'm the only
cardiothoracic here.

304
00:16:40,533 --> 00:16:41,844
Well, what about
one of your residents?

305
00:16:41,868 --> 00:16:43,700
I mean, the tall one
looked semi-competent.

306
00:16:43,769 --> 00:16:45,829
Nottingham and, look,
for all these patients,

307
